idance. The people of whims disagree over their whims, but they agree\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31880,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/prophet-disavows-hawa-bidah\/","url_meta":{"origin":24120,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Whims: The Prophet disavows people of whims, heresies","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to Aisha, \u201cO Aisha! Verily, those who divided their religion and became sects (6:159), they are the people of innovations and whims. They will not repent. I disavow them and they disavow me.\u201d Source: al-Mu'jam\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31823,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/ibn-abbas-quran-whims\/","url_meta":{"origin":24120,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Whims: The Quran casts blame upon lowly desires","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Jawzi reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty did not mention whims in any place in his book but that he cast blame on it.\u201d Source: Dhamm al-Hawa\u0301 1\/36 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0648\u0632\u064a \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639